[Name] LibLazy
[Summary] Convenience functions for D-Bus, HAL and PolicyKit
[Description] LibLazy is a simple and easy to use library that provides convenient \
functions for sending messages over the D-Bus daemon, querying information from HAL \
or asking PolicyKit for a privilege. Its features may grow as needed, though.
[License] GNU Lesser General Public License version 2.1
[Homepage] http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/liblazy
